<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;">
    <center class="wrapper" style="width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding-bottom: 60px;">
        <table class="main-table" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
            <tr>
                <td class="header" style="background-color: #097969; padding: 30px; border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                    <h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; margin: 0; padding: 0;">Password Reset Request</h1>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="content" style="padding: 30px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Dear <%= name %>,</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        We received a request to reset the password for your account.
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        To reset your password, please click the button below:
                    </p>
                    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        <a href="<%= resetPasswordLink %>" class="button" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #097969; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px;">Reset Your Password</a>
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777777; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        This link is valid for a limited time (e.g., 1 hour). If the link expires, you will need to request a new password reset.
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777777; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        Best regards,<br />
                        The Blog Team
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="footer" style="background-color: #eeeeee; padding: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #777777;">
                    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Trend Trails. All rights reserved.
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>
</html>